:-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/339997/逃犯條例-示威者被橡膠子彈擊中險盲-非致命武器-殺傷力強\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F339997%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD%E9%9A%AA%E7%9B%B2-%E9%9D%9E%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E6%AE%BA%E5%82%B7%E5%8A%9B%E5%BC%B7&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=7ac26100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/339997/逃犯條例-示威者被橡膠子彈擊中險盲-非致命武器-殺傷力強</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbfwy1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmbfwy1N.png&h=62dc0825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有網民昨日晚上在FACEBOOK上載數張相片，指是朋友於示威現場被橡膠子彈擊中</span>，並留言：「畀大家睇下朋友被橡膠彈擦面而過，都傷成咁樣！」相片可見傷者的左邊面受傷，留下一道傷口及流血，傷痕很深。<br />\n<br />\n上載相片的網民向《香港01》記者表示，受傷的朋友在立法會衝突中被警方的橡膠子彈射中臉頰，留下一道3厘米傷口，差5厘米便會射中左眼，險盲。她引述傷者說，中彈一刻感到很痛，現仍在港島區一間醫院留醫，<span style=\"color: red;\">但她不便透露更多細節。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男教師傷個眼角 幾偏新聞係現場採訪，呢個傷撚到盲咁濟無記者採訪，無義士拍片作實？ 記者做唔到野 炒撚左去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士點對得住呢位受傷既勇者呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傷得咁重，應該有排未出得院<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/article/【逃犯條例】醫管局指僅1人留醫+疑為港台外判司機-2Perm8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Farticle%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%87%E5%83%851%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%99%E9%86%AB%2B%E7%96%91%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-2Perm8&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=43fc5592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/article/【逃犯條例】醫管局指僅1人留醫+疑為港台外判司機-2Perm8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRqHFHL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRqHFHL.png&h=6e52ce08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得一人？屌又fake news?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f64342fa1544c1cc79e8d2bf3e7f0f621a6ab1","tid":1222402,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"所謂警察精神 就係打人<br />\n我地警隊七犬 暗角打獲<br />\n不但會打婆婆 又會揸波"},{"pid":"d9f28e742909d01e1b6affca7020b99775fde865","tid":1222402,"uid":190464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"入左金鐘 就準備做龜<br />\n開到兩槍 就升隊目"},{"pid":"ccbecc53edd1b99d28d5ada76dc1e3f933551d66","tid":1222402,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4330207a80b8303f5ed4b84950edbfadf811c9","tid":1222402,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988fa60dc855c7e81522b25a4768477a785c3303","tid":1222402,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc97180db1b59f46275536c179380a6d8ff19aad","tid":1222402,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"警察精神<br />\n打撚死人<br />\n打你唔死<br />\n記你老味(母)"},{"pid":"409f25a744c0932af393ca4ad16eb80abfcf3345","tid":1222402,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor